<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>: ١١] ,<span class="c5"> وَأَنْشَدَنَا أَبُو نَصْرٍ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>حَتَّى إِذَا مَا قَصَّرَ الْعَشِيُّ ... عَنْهُ وَقَدْ قَابَلَهُ حُوشِيُّ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُؤَخِّرُ الْعِشَاءَ»</span> ,<span class="c5"> وَالْعِشَاءُ:</span> الصَّلَاةُ الَّتِي بَعْدَ الْمَغْرِبِ ,<span class="c5"> تُدْعَى الْعَتَمَةَ قَالَ الرَّاجِزُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إِذَا الثُّرَيَّا طَلَعَتْ عَشِيًّا ... فَبِعْ لِرَاعِي غَنْمٍ كُسَيَّا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَا كَانَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ يَلْقَى مِنْ شِدَّةِ الْعَيْشِ»</span> , الْعَيْشُ وَالْمَعِيشَةُ الْحَيَاةُ ,<span class="c5"> وَالرَّجُلُ يَعِيشُ بِالْمَعْرُوفِ أَيْ يُعْطَى قَلِيلًا قَالَ رُؤْبَةُ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الرجز]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>حَجَّاجُ مَا سَجْلُكَ بِالْمَعْشُوشِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>يُسْقَيْنَ لَا عَشًّا وَلَا مُصَرَّدَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>⦗٥٧٩⦘<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَأَعْشَشْتُ بِالْقَوْمِ:</span> أَعْجَلْتُهُمْ قَالَ:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلَوْ تُرِكَتْ نَامَتْ وَلَكِنْ أَعَشَّهَا ... أَذًى مِنْ قِلَاصٍ كَالْحَنِيِّ الْمُعَطَّفِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>